Abby,

I believe that Mike Durbin is responsible for delivering the metadata 
that is used for the Avalon items for searching and for display in Virgo.
Some of the metadata about that particular item is included in the 
record that is delivered to me, such as the conductor and the musician, 
and /is/ used for searching, but is not displayed.
other pieces of the metadata for that particular item, is not included 
in the record that is delivered to me, such as the entirety of the notes 
field.

I believe that Mike is also responsible for the code that is used for 
displaying these items in Virgo.   It appears that the conductor and the 
musician are intended to be displayed, but they seem not to be displayed.

-Bob



